name: Sécrétions Magnifiques
description: Infamous for its unique, challenging scent profile, evoking bodily fluids and metallic accords. A provocative and divisive fragrance.

name: I Am Trash – Les Fleurs du Déchet
description: The most wanted fragrance from the end of the world. A perfume created from the unwanted, the discarded, the trash, using upcycled ingredients.

name: Fat Electrician
description: A beautiful and unexpected vetiver fragrance with notes of chestnut cream and olive leaves, evoking a sense of grounded comfort.

name: You Or Someone Like You
description: A fresh, green, and inviting fragrance inspired by the city of Los Angeles and a fictional character.

name: Jasmin et Cigarette
description: A sensual and addictive fragrance that combines the femininity of jasmine with the smoky aroma of a cigarette.

name: Remarkable People
description: A fragrance for the exceptional, the unconventional. A celebration of those who break the mold, with champagne and spicy notes.

name: Hermann A Mes Côtés Me Paraissait Une Ombre
description: A dark, woody, and earthy fragrance, evoking a walk in a damp forest with a mysterious shadow.

name: Divin'Enfant
description: A paradoxical fragrance combining the innocence of orange blossom and marshmallow with the rebellion of tobacco and leather.

name: Like This (Tilda Swinton)
description: A unique and comforting fragrance, inspired by Tilda Swinton's home, with ginger, pumpkin, and immortelle.

name: Putain des Palaces
description: A seductive and sensual fragrance, evoking the scent of a courtesan's boudoir with rose, leather, and powder.

name: Exit The King
description: A modern chypre fragrance, signaling the end of an era and the rise of something new, with moss and soap.

name: The Ghost In The Shell
description: A futuristic and ethereal fragrance, exploring the boundary between human and machine, with synthetic and floral notes.

name: She Was An Anomaly
description: A soft, musky, and powdery fragrance, an ode to individuality and difference.

name: Cologne
description: A fresh, clean, and classic cologne, reimagined with a modern twist.

name: Dangerous Complicity
description: A dangerous and enticing floral-fruity-woody fragrance, full of intrigue.

name: Archives 69
description: A playful and provocative oriental-spicy fragrance, celebrating freedom and sensuality.

name: Attaquer Le Soleil Marquis de Sade
description: A bold and intense amber fragrance, a challenging homage to the Marquis de Sade, with a focus on cistus.

name: 500 Years
description: A rich and exotic oriental-spicy fragrance, celebrating the Renaissance and its discoveries.

name: Soul of My Soul
description: A comforting and intimate musky-amber fragrance, evoking deep connection and warmth.

name: Frustration
description: A gourmand-woody fragrance that explores the feeling of frustration, with notes of vanilla, rum, and chestnut.

name: Clean Suede
description: A soft and clean leather fragrance, combining the supple feel of suede with fresh, delicate notes.

name: Spice Must Flow
description: A powerful and intense oriental-spicy fragrance, inspired by the deserts of Arrakis and its precious spice.

name: Experimentum Crucis
description: A complex and intriguing chypre fragrance, a 'crucial experiment' in scent, with a rose, patchouli, and cumin blend.
